            <div class="px-8 text-right">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Technology-Driven Solutions</h3>
              <p class="text-green-100">Our platform connects users with certified recycling facilities nationwide.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900">Our Solution</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Comprehensive Directory</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Our platform features the most extensive database of certified electronics recycling centers in the United States. We provide detailed information about each facility.</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• Location and contact details</li>
                <li>• Accepted electronics types</li>
                <li>• Recycling certifications</li>
                <li>• Operating hours and fees</li>
                <li>• Special services offered</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Rigorous Verification</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We don't just list any recycling center. Our team conducts thorough research and verification to ensure quality and reliability.</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• R2 and e-Stewards certification checks</li>
                <li>• EPA compliance verification</li>
                <li>• State licensing confirmation</li>
                <li>• Data security protocol validation</li>
                <li>• Environmental impact assessment</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-blue-200 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6">How Our Platform Works</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Search by Location</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Enter your zip code or city to find nearby recycling centers. Our database covers all 50 states with thousands of verified locations.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">2</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Filter by Device Type</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Select the electronics you need to recycle. View centers that accept your specific devices and any special requirements.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">3</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Get Detailed Information</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Access contact details, hours, pricing, and preparation instructions. Make informed decisions about your recycling options.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Visual break with impact image -->
        <div class="relative mb-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/corporate-meeting.jpg" alt="Team working on environmental solutions" class="w-full h-64 object-cover">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/80 to-transparent flex items-center">
            <div class="px-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Making a Difference Together</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-100">Our platform connects millions with responsible recycling solutions nationwide.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900">Our Impact</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-green-50 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
